#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This module allows you to select a style for the buttons and borders around "
"the windows."
msgstr "Ta modul vam omogoča izbiro sloga za gumbe in meje oken."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Window Decoration Configuration Module</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Konfiguracijski modul dekoracij oken</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Window Decoration Configuration Module</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Konfiguracijski modul dekoracij oken</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a window decoration style from the preview list, or download a new "
"style using the <guibutton>Get New Window Decorations</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Izberite slog dekoracije oken s seznama za predogled ali prenesite nov slog "
"z gumbom <guibutton>Pridobi nove dekoracije oken</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "The default window decoration is called <quote>Breeze</quote>."
msgstr "Privzeta dekoracija oken se imenuje <quote>Vetrič</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each style has a different look, but also a different <quote>feel</quote>. "
"Some have (sometimes invisible) <quote>resize</quote> borders all around the "
"edge, which make resizing easier but moving more difficult. Some have no "
"borders on certain edges."
msgstr ""
"Vsak slog ima drugačen izgled, pa tudi drugačen <quote>občutek</quote>. "
"Nekateri imajo (včasih nevidno) <quote>raztegljive</quote> meje okoli in "
"okoli robov, kar olajša spreminjanje velikosti, a oteži premikanje okna. "
"Nekateri nimajo mej na določenih robovih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You are encouraged to experiment with the different styles until you find "
"one which best suits your pattern of work."
msgstr ""
"Spodbujamo vas k eksperimentiranju z različnimi slogi, dokler ne najdete "
"takšnega, ki najbolje ustreza vašemu vzorcu dela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the preview of each style you find a <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> configure button to open configuration dialogs for the "
"decoration."
msgstr ""
"V predogledu vsakega sloga najdete <inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject> gumb za konfiguracijo, s katerim odprete konfiguracijska "
"pogovorna okna za dekoracijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options in this configuration dialog are applied to all windows. Some "
"window decorations (&eg; <quote>Breeze</quote>) provide a <guilabel>Window-"
"Specific Overrides</guilabel> tab. On this tab you can change the border "
"size and the visibility of the window titlebar for particular windows."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti v tem konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu se uporabljajo za vsa okna. "
"Nekatere dekoracije oken (&eg; <quote>Vetrič</quote>) ponujajo zavihek "
"<guilabel>Ročno nastavljanje oken</guilabel>. Na tem zavihku lahko "
"spremenite velikost obrobe in vidnost naslovne vrstice okna za specifična "
"okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Different options for particular windows you find in the &systemsettings; "
"module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/windowspecific\">Window Rules</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Različne možnosti za določena okna najdete v &systemsettings; modul <ulink "
"url=\"help:/kcontrol/windowspecific\">Pravila oken</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For accessibility purposes, some window decorations support extra wide "
"borders. If this is available, you can also choose a <guilabel>Window border "
"size</guilabel> here. The large borders are easier to see for low vision "
"users, and easier to grab for people with limited mobility or difficulty "
"using a mouse."
msgstr ""
"Za namene dostopnosti nekatere dekoracije oken podpirajo zelo široke obrobe. "
"Če je to na voljo, lahko tukaj izberete tudi <guilabel>Velikost obrobe okna</"
"guilabel>. Velike obrobe so lažje vidne za slabovidne uporabnike in jih "
"lažje primejo osebe z omejeno mobilnostjo ali težavami pri uporabi miške."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are interested in creating your own window decoration, you can learn "
"more about it <ulink url=\"https://develop.kde.org/docs/plasma/aurorae/\">in "
"this tutorial</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če vas zanima ustvarjanje lastne dekoracije oken, lahko izveste več o tem "
"<ulink url=\"https://develop.kde.org/docs/extend/plasma/aurorae/\">učbeniku</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Decorations"
msgstr "Dekoracija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In this dialog you can change the decoration of the window. The available "
"options depend on the selected style."
msgstr ""
"V tem pogovornem oknu lahko spremenite dekoracijo okna. Razpoložljive "
"možnosti so odvisne od izbranega sloga."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Breeze Decoration Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti dekoracije Vetrič</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Breeze Decoration Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti dekoracije Vetrič</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Titlebar Buttons"
msgstr "Gumbi naslovne vrstice"

# &eg;
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This page allows you to customize the button location on the titlebar. You "
"can drag buttons &eg; the <guilabel>Application menu</guilabel> into the "
"titlebar, remove them or drag around the buttons until you have the order "
"that makes you comfortable."
msgstr ""
"Ta stran vam omogoča prilagajanje lokacije gumba v naslovni vrstici. Lahko "
"povlečete gumbe &eg; <guilabel>Meni aplikacij</guilabel> v naslovno vrstico, "
"jih odstranite ali povlečete med gumbi, dokler ne najdete vrstnega reda, ki "
"vam ustreza."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Button Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Možnosti gumbov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Button Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Možnosti gumbov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable <guilabel>Close windows by double clicking the window menu button</"
"guilabel> to have an additional option to the Close button or if you have "
"removed the Close button from the titlebar."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite <guilabel>Zapiranje oken z dvojnim klikom na gumb menija</"
"guilabel>, da imate poleg gumba Zapri še dodatno možnost zapiranja ali če "
"ste gumb Zapri odstranili iz naslovne vrstice."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the <guilabel>Show titlebar buttons tooltips</guilabel> item if you "
"want to see the default tooltips when you hover the titlebar buttons with "
"the mouse pointer."
msgstr ""
"Odkljukajte element <guilabel>V naslovni vrstici prikaži opise orodij "
"gumbov</guilabel>, če želite videti privzete opise orodij, ko z miškinim "
"kazalcem lebdite čez gumbe v naslovni vrstici."

